  "title": "School Admin Assistant #West Coast Rd",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Working Hour</strong></u></p><ul><li>Mondays to Thursdays: 9:30am to 6:30pm, inclusive of 0.5 hr lunch break</li><li>Fridays: 10 am to 6:30pm, inclusive of 0.5 hr lunch break</li><li>Service not required on Saturdays, Sundays and gazetted public holidays</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirement</strong></u></p><ul><li>At least GCE ‘N’ Level Certificate or its equivalent</li><li><strong>Valid first aid with CPR certification</strong> </li><li>Proficient with Microsoft Office </li><li>Good communication and inter-personal skills with patience and ability to remain calm during challenging situations </li><li>Possess initiative, good problem-solving skills and ability to multitask</li><li>Able to work independently and collaborate in a team</li><li>3 years of similar working experience in a school environment</li><li>Minimally 3 years of relevant experience in administration</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Scope</strong></u><br />🖥️ <strong>Front Desk & Reception:</strong> Answer and transfer phone calls; attend to walk-in parents, students, and vendors.</p><p><p>🔑 <strong>Key Management:</strong> Issue keys to staff requiring access to special rooms.</p></p><p><p>🏥 <strong>Sick Bay Support:</strong> Record details of and attend to students who are unwell in the sick bay.</p></p><p><p>📞 <strong>Parent Communication:</strong> Contact parents to provide updates on students who are unwell.</p></p><p><p>📝 <strong>Early Dismissal Logging:</strong> Record details of students leaving school early due to sickness or medical appointments; ensure completion of the Early Dismissal form.</p></p><p><p>🧸 <strong>Lost & Found Coordination:</strong> Record lost & found items in the designated form and track movements at the end of each school term.</p></p><p><p>📦 <strong>Delivery Handling:</strong> Receive delivered items and notify relevant staff for collection from the General Office.</p></p><p><p>📋 <strong>Testimonial Tracking:</strong> Collate and maintain a list of students who have not collected their testimonials.</p></p><p><p>👕 <strong>Uniform Loan Administration:</strong> Manage the loaning and return of school uniforms to students.</p></p><p><p>📬 <strong>Material Distribution:</strong> Distribute mailers and any other required materials.</p></p><p><p>🍱 <strong>Food Coupon Management:</strong> Prepare and count food coupons for payment as needed.</p></p><p><p>📌 <strong>Ad-Hoc Duties:</strong> Perform any additional administrative tasks as assigned.</p></p>",
